        "first_seen": "2026-05-02",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-02",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_007",
        "text": "I'm worried I'll get practice questions wrong and lose motivation completely",
        "tone": "scared",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-02",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-02",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_008",
        "text": "Finding myself in The Namesake—the main character's struggle between two cultures mirrors my own experience of growing up Marathi at home but learning everything in English. It's what makes stories so relatable.",
        "tone": "content",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-05",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-05",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_009",
        "text": "I want to write fiction after exams—it feels like the creative outlet I'm putting on hold for now.",
        "tone": "hopeful",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-05",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-05",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_010",
        "text": "I have no real study plan. I just read the first paragraph, get bored, then panic. It's the same pattern every time.",
        "tone": "anxious",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-07",
